body.name: USB C to Lightning Cable [Apple MFi Certified] 3 Pack 6FT iPhone Charger Fast Charging Power Delivery Charging Cord Compatible with iPhone 14/13/12/11/XS/XR/X/8/iPad and More
features: 🎊【PD Fast Charging and Data Transfer】: The USB C to lightning cables support power delivery fast charging for iPhone 14,13, iPhone 12, 12 Pro, 12 Pro Max, 11, 11 Pro, 11 Pro Max. It also supports data transfer speeds of up to 480Mbps Note: You will need a USB-C port wall charger for fast charging

🎊【Apple MFi Certified】: Apple MFi Certified USB to lightning cable guaranteed no pop-up warning messages. These iphone fast charger cables use the newest C94 lightning end design for fast charging. Built-in overvoltage protection ensure your iPhone/iPad devices are charged safely and takes the worry out of it

🎊【Super Durability and Flexibility】: Premium and understated color combinations to take your position to the next level. The iphone charging cables are made of top-rated material and coated with premium TPE, which last 3X longer than other iphone charger cord and proven to withstand over 10,000 bends in strict laboratory tests

🎊【Wide Compatibility】: USB C to iPhone cable supports PD fast charge, for iPhone 14/13 Pro/13 Pro Max/13 Mini/12/12 Pro/12 Pro Max/12 Mini/11/11 Pro/11 Pro Max/XS/ Max/XS/XR/X/8 Plus/8 and iPhone 7 Plus/7 etc. Wide range of adaptability with premium vibe colors to make your device stand out!

🎊【What You Get】: 3pack 6ft USB-C to lightning fast cables, which have a hassle-free lifetime warranty. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us, we will resolve your issue as soon as possible
